Package org.jtestdb.selenium.tstmod

Package for SetTestMode which provides capability to use make Selenium add of remove elements from the DOM of a web-page under test (WUT).

These elements may then be used as flags to indicate a page is under-test and test-friendly Javascript or Selenium code may be used to implement conditions necessary for tests.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SetTestMode
    Class to set a web-page under test via a test-mode-element being added to some 'normal' element within the page.

Package org.jtestdb.selenium.tstmod Description

Package for SetTestMode which provides capability to use make Selenium add of remove elements from the DOM of a web-page under test (WUT).

These elements may then be used as flags to indicate a page is under-test and test-friendly Javascript or Selenium code may be used to implement conditions necessary for tests.
